Group Reflection :
Being in ICT profession requires a curious mind and the person skill in solving real-world problems.
ICT professionals often work on innovative solutions to improve efficiency, enhance user experience and drive economic growth.
An individual need to have passion for their work in order to be committed in executing their daily task efficiently as an employee of an ICT industry.

My Own Reflection :
The "Overview of ICT Jobs in Industry" industry talk made me realize how quickly the ICT field is evolving and what skills are necessary to stay up to date. 
I discovered how crucial it is to remain flexible and never stop learning.
This session inspired me to explore ways to apply my skills meaningfully and highlighted the broader impact of ICT on society and industry.
